cs.PL, cs.SE, cs.LO, cs.FL, cs.CR 

The paper discusses the development of abstract interpreters, which is a topic in programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). It also addresses theoretical issues related to correctness (cs.LO) and practical issues related to automation (cs.FL). Finally, it discusses proof techniques (cs.CR) for verifying the correctness of abstract computation models.
